Police have asked the public to come forward with any information that could assist in locating the businessman. CAPE TOWN An Athlone businessman has still not been found after he was allegedly kidnapped.Naushad Khan was allegedly abducted by six armed suspects on Monday evening outside his shop.The suspects also took an undisclosed sum of cash.The police s Andre Traut says: The circumstances surrounding an armed robbery and kidnapping are being investigated by Athlone police. Any person with information is kindly requested to Crime Stop on 08600 10111. (Edited by Masechaba Sefularo)